data.description:
Wonderful home with new windows and an open concept layout. The formal living area, large dining area, & spacious family room with a rock fireplace creates a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is well-equipped with a new dishwasher, refrigerator, stainless electric stove, & microwave. Fantastic laundry room that can also be used as a home office or hobby room. The backyard is manageable with a tall metal fence, metal storage shed, & covered patio. Close to shopping, restaurants, & school!
